			<CASNumber>1333-74-0</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Green hydrogen is hydrogen fuel that is created using renewable energy sources, making it a clean energy carrier. It is considered potent in the clean energy sector due to its environmentally friendly production method, which results in a reduced carbon footprint. Green hydrogen serves as a renewable, scalable, and versatile raw material for various industrial processes, including the manufacturing of steel, cement, fertilizers, fuels, and chemicals. It is particularly significant in transportation, where it has the potential to greatly decrease greenhouse gas emissions. Despite its benefits, green hydrogen currently represents a small fraction of hydrogen production, with the majority being 'gray' hydrogen produced from natural gas.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">绿氢是利用可再生能源生产的氢燃料，使其成为清洁能源载体。由于其环保的生产方法，它被认为在清洁能源领域具有强大的影响力，从而减少了碳足迹。绿氢是一种可再生、可扩展和多用途的原材料，用于各种工业过程，包括钢铁、水泥、化肥、燃料和化学品的制造。它在交通运输领域尤为重要，有可能大大减少温室气体排放。尽管有好处，但绿色氢气目前只占氢气生产的一小部分，其中大部分是由天然气生产的“灰色”氢气。</common:generalComment>
